Simple, fast and clean app, that allows you to watch Tom Scott’s videos. Get notified whenever a new video is uploaded to keep up to date.

The app was produced to give the best user experience possible. Keeping it clutter free, you can concentrate on the content and not get distracted by other YouTube videos and ads that don’t interest you.

This is an unofficial Tom Scott app, developed by Feisty. Feisty specializes in producing high quality apps for the most popular YouTube artists in the world. For enquiries, feedback or anything else, please contact us using the developer email.

